{"tid":1949304,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"國際戰線唔係Trump助選團隊","createTime":"2020-03-29T14:08:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-30T10:56:24.000Z","uid":134071,"like":39,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"d158ee2ed511d8dfcee2c8c0619adada90b6c869","tid":1949304,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T14:08:16.000Z","msg":"Twitter 屌緊侵侵送曬啲防護衣比中國<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1948990/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1948990/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n見到有人話要係twitter幫Trump辯護, 我覺得唔駛.<br />\n<br />\n要留意, 國際戰線 唔係Trump助選團隊, 亦唔係美國民主黨既助選團隊.<br />\n<strong>國際戰線(特別在twitter) 係要拉攏更多人支持香港, 團結反中共政權. 團結對象, 不分左中右.</strong> &nbsp;<br />\n(有關對個別政客的個人偏好, 最好留係連登同facebook講.)<br />\n<br />\n係Trump呢件事, 手足可以借d耳唱衰中共, 但唔駛刻幫Trump辯護.<br />\n<br />\n<strong>共和黨Solomon Yue有份幫Trump助選, 但佢都警告香港人不要介入美國兩黨鬥爭, 不要 「拉一派打一派」. 因為, 香港人需要美國兩黨的共同支持.</strong> &nbsp;大家要明白Solomon Yue手足的苦心. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1695914/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1695914/page/1</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://na.cx/i/2DwXvot.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2DwXvot.jpg&h=2e328b23&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://na.cx/i/BehWLW9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBehWLW9.jpg&h=1f618b5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e5e19c255b267205a2edbbf116137ff39fdd6c7e","tid":1949304,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T14:11:07.000Z","msg":"[更新版]到底大家撐唔撐港台<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1949128\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1949128</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5d81331654d6a5e99119519a786379eacda6b11c","tid":1949304,"uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T14:12:23.000Z","msg":"我自己暫時都傾向Trump連任<br />\n但twitter最大功用, 係幫香港拉攏最多盟友, 不分左中右<br />\n<br />\n最近, 美國兩黨合作提案譴責「中共」抗疫, 證明反共不分左中右. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1941889/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1941889/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"c5b26b3fa191bacfb10d82e014519af12fcebd51","tid":1949304,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T14:16:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"365ec7c4757abc7594e2b3cbaf45b2ebb3953434","tid":1949304,"uid":108374,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T14:18:10.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"ecaf751843abe8683a6ff7b4ba15a9c3f9c4c083","tid":1949304,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"365ec7c4757abc7594e2b3cbaf45b2ebb3953434","tid":1949304,"uid":108374,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T14:18:10.000Z","msg":"幫推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T14:21:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"280c01bd45f324775f234471d9d831dba17c6dcc","tid":1949304,"uid":261699,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T14:25:57.000Z","msg":"應該講<br />\n我地目標要美國以至其他國家幫都好<br />\n並唔係要果個國家執政黨幫<br />\n而係希望人地會傾全國之力嚟幫<br />\n即使唔幫都唔緊要<br />\n起碼要對中共有所警戒"},{"pid":"f9033e72d71e215d10fdeceef622424220a66b2f","tid":1949304,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"280c01bd45f324775f234471d9d831dba17c6dcc","tid":1949304,"uid":261699,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T14:25:57.000Z","msg":"